# Summary
Datazoom integration enables video publishers to send raw, standardized video events to Amplitude, allowing them to centralize and standardize video data for improved observability and optimization. Setup requires copying an Amplitude API key and configuring a Datazoom Connector with options for sampling rate and field redirection.

